so you can go to the reformatory!

635
00:38:06,117 --> 00:38:08,452
I didn't break any laws.

636
00:38:11,789 --> 00:38:13,791
Yu-ri, it's okay. Stop crying.

637
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:17,086
-Calm down. Can you stand up?
-I didn't do anything wrong.

638
00:38:17,169 --> 00:38:19,547
WOORI CONVALESCENT HOSPITAL

639
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:20,840
It's okay.

640
00:38:28,222 --> 00:38:30,516
YEONHWA DISTRICT COURT

641
00:38:32,768 --> 00:38:34,228
