because of her abusive father.

644
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:43,738
So she ran away and joined a gang.

645
00:38:43,821 --> 00:38:45,781
Shouldn't you be asking
why she joined them

646
00:38:45,865 --> 00:38:48,284
rather than being upset that she did?

647
00:38:50,244 --> 00:38:52,663
Judge Sim,
I've been wondering for a while now.

648
00:38:53,289 --> 00:38:54,957
Just out of curiosity,

649
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:58,127
why do you hate young offenders so much?

650
00:38:59,503 --> 00:39:00,338
What?

651
00:39:00,421 --> 00:39:02,798
Why do you always hurt them with words

652
00:39:02,882 --> 00:39:06,427
and always try so hard to see
if you can find any fault in them?

653
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:08,012
Why are you so mad at them?

654
00:39:08,095 --> 00:39:09,430
Because they're criminals.

655
00:39:11,682 --> 00:39:14,643
They dared to commit a crime…

656
00:39:16,771 --> 00:39:18,606
at such a young age.

657
00:39:23,152 --> 00:39:24,528
Let me ask you something.

658
00:39:25,821 --> 00:39:27,490
Is this something to be so upset about?

659
00:39:27,573 --> 00:39:29,909
Why are you always on their side?

660
00:39:30,534 --> 00:39:32,078
Do they have something on you?

661
00:39:32,161 --> 00:39:34,330
-Judge Sim!
-What is it then?

662
00:39:36,415 --> 00:39:38,334
Why do you keep butting in on my case?

663
00:39:42,588 --> 00:39:43,798
Come on out!

664
00:39:46,467 --> 00:39:49,512
Come out. Come out, you bastard!

665
00:39:51,305 --> 00:39:52,515
Come out!

666
00:39:53,599 --> 00:39:55,684
So I borrowed some money
from your teacher.

667
00:39:55,768 --> 00:39:58,521
It's not a big deal
when you're doing business.

668
00:39:58,604 --> 00:40:00,356
How dare you yell at me?

669
00:40:00,439 --> 00:40:01,899
-Please, Dad.
-Come out!

670
00:40:01,982 --> 00:40:03,567
-Come out, you bastard!
-I'm sorry!

671
00:40:03,651 --> 00:40:05,403
-Come out!
-I'm sorry!

672
00:40:05,486 --> 00:40:06,946
Come out! You bastard!

673
00:40:07,613 --> 00:40:10,157
Come out!

674
00:40:10,241 --> 00:40:11,826
Come out! You bastard!

675
00:40:11,909 --> 00:40:16,205
