00:40:55,786 --> 00:40:58,247
Everyone criticizes juvenile offenders.

684
00:40:59,165 --> 00:41:01,125
It's just us judges

685
00:41:02,460 --> 00:41:03,919
who can give them a second chance.

686
00:41:06,547 --> 00:41:09,884
