688
00:42:10,319 --> 00:42:12,738
-Trial starts in thirty minutes.
-Okay.

689
00:42:19,036 --> 00:42:21,372
What's wrong with this?

690
00:42:21,914 --> 00:42:23,332
The battery must be dead.

691
00:42:23,415 --> 00:42:25,000
I'll go get new ones.

692
00:42:25,084 --> 00:42:26,544
-Hurry up.
-Okay.

693
00:42:27,253 --> 00:42:29,547
-You're getting sloppy.
