743
00:45:41,071 --> 00:45:43,824
I'm Detective Ko Gang-sik from Yeonhwa PD,
Women and Juvenile Affairs.

744
00:45:43,907 --> 00:45:45,117
POLICE STATION

745
00:45:45,200 --> 00:45:47,202
